      "content": "<p>Hi everyone, the livestream for Science x AI Summit 2026 (Palo Alto) will begin in about 3 hours.</p>\n<p>The first session will feature several excellent AI x Math talks, including Prof. Terence Tao’s talk on SAIR Competitions at 10:15 AM PT. We warmly invite everyone to watch the livestream and share it with anyone who may be interested.</p>\n<p>Agenda:<br>\n<a href=\"https://sair.foundation/events/science-ai-summit-2026\">https://sair.foundation/events/science-ai-summit-2026</a></p>\n<p>Watch livestreaming on Youtube:<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XSK11zBg7TQ\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XSK11zBg7TQ</a></p>\n<div class=\"youtube-video message_inline_image\"><a data-id=\"XSK11zBg7TQ\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XSK11zBg7TQ\"><img src=\"/external_content/d82d36fd90bb963fceb330ea317707dfe350a7eb/68747470733a2f2f692e7974696d672e636f6d2f76692f58534b31317a42673754512f6d7164656661756c742e6a7067\"></a></div>",
